Movie.create("category_id"=>1, "description"=>"This tragicomedy is a self-ironic portrait of a young man who drops out of university and ends up wandering the streets of the city he lives in: Berlin. The film deals with the desire to participate in life and the difficulty to find one's place. Black and white, tragic and funny, Oh Boy! is a winning debut from director Jan Ole Gerster.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/de/images/products/324347/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1362778663_Lovefilmde324347_.jpg", "title"=>"Oh Boy", "year"=>2013)

Movie.create("category_id"=>1, "description"=>"Steven Spielberg's Academy Award-winning political biopic stars Daniel Day-Lewis as America's 16th president Abraham Lincoln. The film focuses on the last few months of Lincoln's life, which not only saw the ending of slavery despite dogged opposition from many inside Lincoln's own cabinet, but also the Union victory in the American Civil War. The supporting cast includes Sally Field as Lincoln's wife Mary, Joseph Gordon-Levitt as Lincoln's son Robert and Tommy Lee Jones as Radical Republican Congressional leader Thaddeus Stevens. Daniel Day-Lewis won the Academy Award, a Golden Globe and a BAFTA for Best Actor for his performance.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/195313/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1375293896_Lovefilmgb195313_.jpg", "title"=>"Lincoln", "year"=>2012)

Movie.create("category_id"=>1, "description"=>"Mysterious and mythical motorcycle racer, Luke, (Ryan Gosling) desperately tries to connect with a former lover, Romina, (Eva Mendes) who secretly gave birth to the stunt riderâ€™s son. In an attempt to provide for his new family, Luke commits a series of bank robberies aided by his superior riding ability. The stakes rise as Luke is put on a collision course with an ambitious police officer, Avery Cross, (Bradley Cooper) looking to quickly move up the ranks in a police department riddled with corruption.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/209804/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1372102452_Lovefilmgb209804_.jpg", "title"=>"The Place Beyond the Pines", "year"=>2012)

Movie.create("category_id"=>0, "description"=>"In the futurist action thriller Looper, time travel will be invented - but it will be illegal and only available on the black market. When the mob wants to get rid of someone, they will send their target 30 years into the past, where a looper - a hired gun, like Joe - is waiting to mop up. Joe is getting rich and life is good... until the day the mob decides to \"close the loop,\" sending back Joe's future self for assassination.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/198125/packshot._UX500_PJStripe-HD-Only-500px,TopLeft,0,0_UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1356722311_Lovefilmgb198125_.jpg", "title"=>"Looper", "year"=>2012)

Movie.create("category_id"=>2, "description"=>"The story of an Indian boy named Pi, a zookeeper's son who finds himself in the company of a hyena, zebra, orangutan, and a Bengal tiger after a shipwreck sets them adrift in the Pacific Ocean.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/188538/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1376417045_Lovefilmgb188538_.jpg", "title"=>"Life of Pi", "year"=>2012)

Movie.create("category_id"=>3, "description"=>"Heart-warming Pixar animated tale about a robot who accidentally discovers the way to save planet Earth. 700 years after humanity has left Earth, WALL-E (Waste Allocation Load Lifter Earth-Class) fills his days collecting rubbish, and anything else that takes his fancy, trying to fend off the boredom of his lot. But unknowingly, the tiny tube-eyed robot has discovered a secret that could make the once beautiful planet habitable again, enabling humankind to return. One day, Eve, a search robot, lands on Earth in a cloud of dust, and WALL-E is smitten. When she realizes the importance of his find, she sets out to tell the remaining humans, eager to let them know the planet can be saved. But WALL-E, after centuries of being alone, can't bear to see her go, and hitches a ride through the cosmos on an adventure his memory banks will never forget.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/216504/packshot._UX500_PJStripe-HD-Only-500px,TopLeft,0,0_UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1366222750_Lovefilmgb216504_.jpg", "title"=>"WALL-E", "year"=>2008)

Movie.create("category_id"=>0, "description"=>"Mystery crime drama starring Tom Cruise and Rosamund Pike. Adapted from a novel in Lee Child's best-selling crime series, the film sees Cruise in the title role as an ex-military policeman turned vigilante drifter who is called in to investigate after an expert sniper takes the lives of five random victims. When the authorities pull in former army sniper, James Barr (Joseph Sikora), they are certain they have the perpetrator, but Barr believes he's been set up and asks that Jack Reacher (Cruise) be assigned to the case. At first, Reacher is weary of Barr but after some thorough investigation he is led to believe there is an unseen force pulling the strings of the investigation and he's determined to get to the truth.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/193566/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1364926515_Lovefilmgb193566_.jpg", "title"=>"Jack Reacher", "year"=>2012)

Movie.create("category_id"=>3, "description"=>"Romantic comedy starring Reese Witherspoon, Owen Wilson and Paul Rudd. Former athlete Lisa (Witherspoon) meets troubled business executive George (Rudd) at a bad time. While Lisa is facing a difficult transition in her life, feeling past her athletic prime and questioning her current relationship with egotistical baseball player Manny (Wilson), George is facing the prospect of financial ruin as his father's company is subject to a federal investigation for shady dealing. But can romance blossom despite the odds? And how do you know who is 'the one'? Jack Nicholson co-stars as George's father, Charles.", "image_url"=>"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/G/01/lovefilm/gb/images/products/165559/packshot._UX140_CR0,0,140,200_V1349719668_Lovefilmgb165559_.jpg", "title"=>"How Do You Know", "year"=>2010)

